<exercises><title>More Tangent Lines</title>
      <exercisegroup cols="3">
        <introduction>
    <figure><title></title>
      <interactive desmos="62fh8p0t3z"
                width="150%" aspect="2:1" />
      <caption> To check your work graph the curve, the point of tangency, and  your line on the axes above.</caption>
    </figure>
          <p>
            Find an equation of the line tangent to the graph of each
            equation at each of the indicated points.
          </p>
          <p>
            In some cases there  is more more than one tangent line.
          </p>
        </introduction>
        <exercise>
